---
import { ArrowRight, Phone, Sparkles } from "lucide-react";

const badges = [
  "Diagnóstico DiSa",
  "Prototipo conceptual",
  "Entrega por hitos",
];
---

<section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-20 animate-slide-up">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
        {badges.map((badge, index) => (
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 text-primary text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 animate-scale-in"
            style={`animation-delay: ${0.1 + index * 0.1}s;`}
          >
            <Sparkles className="w-3 h-3" />
            {badge}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-sora text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-slide-up">
        Software a la medida con{" "}
        <span class="text-gradient-primary">claridad y método</span>
      </h1>

      <p
        class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in"
        style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
      >
        En DiSa transformamos necesidades reales en sistemas que sí se entregan:
        con alcance definido, prototipo conceptual y ejecución por hitos.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s;"
      >
        <a
          href="/contacto?tipo=llamada"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-gradient-primary hover:opacity-90 text-primary-foreground font-semibold px-8 py-3"
        >
          <Phone className="w-4 h-4" />
          Agendar llamada inicial
        </a>
        <a
          href="/servicios"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-primary/30 hover:bg-primary/10 px-8 py-3 font-semibold"
        >
          Ver servicios
          <ArrowRight className="w-4 h-4" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
